<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist William W. Pascoe, III</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>

<img src="/townhall/columnists/colm.gif">






</center>





<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-pascoe.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>

<center>
<h2>William W. Pascoe, III</h2>
</center>


<p>

<!insert photo here>

