<head>
<title>Taxes</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<img src="/atr/atr_logo.gif">
<h2>The Dole Tax Cut Plan<br>
What does it mean for you?</h2>
</center>
<form action="/townhall/scripts/dole96.cgi" method="post">
<input type="text" name="income" size="8"> <b>What is your income?</b><p>

<b>What is your filing status?</b><p>
<ul>
<input type="radio" name="status" checked value="single"> Single<br>
<input type="radio" name="status" value="jointly"> Married filing jointly or Qualifying Widower(er)<br>
<input type="radio" name="status" value="separately"> Married filing separately<br>
<input type="radio" name="status" value="head"> Head of Household<p>
</ul>
<input type="text" name="children" size="2"> <b>Number of children</b> (The Dole-Kemp Tax Cut Plan includes a $500 per child tax credit)<p> 
<input type="submit" name="submit" value="Tax me less!">
</body>
