<html>
<head>
<title>Flat Tax Calculation -- ATR</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor=#FFFFF>
<center><img src="atr_logo.gif" alt="American for Tax Reform"><br>
<p>
</center>
<hr width=40%>
<p>
<center>
<table border=5 cellpadding=10>
<tr>
<td>
<center>
Armey-Shelby Flat Tax Form<p>
</center>
<form action="/townhall/scripts/new.cgi" method="post">
<input type ="hidden" name="outfile" value="/usr/users/www-user/output/atr/flattax">
<b>1.</b> What is your annual income? <input size=10 name="INCOME"><p>
<b>2.</b> What is your filing status?<br>
<dl>
<dd><input type="radio" name="TYPE" value="married" checked> Married filing jointly<br>
<dd><input type="radio" name="TYPE" value="single"> Single<br>
<dd><input type="radio" name="TYPE" value="singleh"> Single, head of household<P>
</dl>

<b>3.</b> How many dependent children?
<input type="textarea" size="2" name="KIDS"> 


</td>
</tr>
</table><p>
